<HEADLINE>
FT  13 OCT 94 / UK Company News: Bulgin 77% ahead
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
AF Bulgin, the electrical components manufacturer, reported a 77 per cent
rise in interim pre-tax profits from Pounds 280,000 to Pounds 497,000.
Turnover for the half year to July 31 was 15 per cent ahead, at Pounds 9.03m
(Pounds 7.84m).
Mr Ronald Bulgin, chairman, said that all parts of the group had performed
well in what had been the most profitable half year for a number of years.
Earnings per share were 1.26p (1p).
