PepsiCo, the US soft drinks and fast-food company, brought cheer to its
shareholders yesterday with quarterly figures suggesting it was fighting off
the threat to its core Pepsi-Cola brand from own-label cola drinks.
The news from its fast-food restaurant businesses, however, was less
