investment capital group, and advised by Coopers &amp; Lybrand and Edge and
Ellison in Birmingham.
Strensham, which will now trade under the TakeaBreak name, is situated on
both sides of the M5 motorway, and employs 209 full-time staff and 65
part-timers, catering for 6m visitors annually.
3i led the equity element of the total finance requirement of Pounds 16.8m,
providing Pounds 4m.
