FT  12 OCT 94 / Jobs to be lost at BR
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Unions expect to be told next week that more than 1,500 white-collar workers
will lose their jobs at British Rail Infrastructure Services over the next
six months as it is split into 20 separate companies prior to privatisation.
